## Full license texts

The complete text of each license is available at the locations listed above
and at the following canonical URLs:

- GNU AGPL v3.0: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.txt  
- CERN-OHL-S v2.0: https://ohwr.org/cern_ohl_s_v2.txt  
- CC BY-SA 4.0: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/legalcode  

For the avoidance of doubt, the AGPL v3.0 full license text is reproduced
in `/firmware/LICENSE` and in the `Paramo` branch `/LICENSE`.
The CERN-OHL-S v2.0 full license text is reproduced in `/hardware/LICENSE`.
